    "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:307",
    "titles": {
      "en": "Camels lost to fulfilling obligations"
    },
    "verse_count": 3,
    "verse_start_index": 2036,
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ],
    "verses": [
      {
        "index": 2037,
        "local_index": 1,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:307:1",
        "relations": null,
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/446/564",
        "text": [
          "٤٤٦. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام) لِغَالِبِ بْنِ صَعْصَعَةَ أَبِی الْفَرَزْدَقِ، فِی كَلَامٍ دَارَ بَيْنَهُمَا: مَا فَعَلَتْ إِبِلُكَ الْكثِيرَةُ؟"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "446. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said to Ghālib ibn Ṣa‘ṣa‘ah, the father of al-Farazdaq (the famous Arabic poet) during a conversation between them: What about the large number of your camels?"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2038,
        "local_index": 2,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:307:2",
        "relations": null,
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/446/565",
        "text": [
          "قال: ذَعْذَعَتْها الحُقُوقُ يا أميرالمؤمنين."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "The man replied: They have been swept away by (discharging of) obligations, O’ Amīr al-mu’minīn!"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2039,
        "local_index": 3,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:307:3",
        "relations": null,
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/446/566",
        "text": [
          "فَقَالَ (عليه السلام) : ذَاكَ أَحْمَدُ سُبُلِهَا."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "Whereupon Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: That is the most praiseworthy way of (losing) them."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "index": "nahj-al-balagha:3:307",
